-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack glom-1.12.7-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./glom-1.12.7-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/glom-1.12.7-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/glom-1.12.7-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libglom1.12-devel-1.12.7-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libglom1.12_0-1.12.7-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/python-glom1.12-1.12.7-X.tar.bz2

